Why `AddRef`? @amitiuttarwar suggestion can be accomplished with
```diff
         explicit NodesSnapshot(const CConnman& connman)
+            : m_nodes_copy(WITH_LOCK(connman.cs_vNodes, return connman.vNodes))
         {
-            LOCK(connman.cs_vNodes);
