comments.body:
Perhaps beyond the scope of this PR, but it may be better if [`Release()`](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/71a85fbd09b5a450edc53a8ba4131f32e7136ca7/src/net.h#L630) asserted that the count is valid:
```
void Release()
{
    assert(nRefCount > 0);
    nRefCount--;
}
```
The count validity is asserted in `GetRefCount()` but it would be better to catch the malefactor in the act :).

